metadata.name: Farewell to Queen Elizabeth II 1
metadata.description:
The artwork is created with artificial intelligence engine.


A single artwork open edition for everyone to hold as a keepsake for the beloved queen of the United Kingdom. A beautiful farewell to the Queen Elizabeth II, in an artificial way.


Born: April 21, 1926, Bruton Street, London, United Kingdom

Died: September 8, 2022, Balmoral Castle, United Kingdom (Age 96)


Elizabeth II is the Queen of the United Kingdom and 14 other Commonwealth realms. Elizabeth was born in Mayfair, London, as the first child of the Duke and Duchess of York. Her father acceded to the throne in 1936 upon the abdication of his brother, King Edward VIII, making Elizabeth the heir presumptive.
